No. 269,

October Term, 1945.

Sabin et al. v. Home Owners' Loan Corp. et al.; and *856Sabin et al. v. Home Owners' Loan Corp. et al. No. 952,

October Term, 1945.

March 31, 1947.

The motions for leave to file second petitions for rehearing are denied.

The Chief Justice and Mr. Justice Jackson took no part in the consideration or decision of these applications.

329 U. S. 823.
